data.enText: one of several parts of which sth is made

data.chText: 政府计划的重要组成部分是…
data.enText: Key components of the government's plan are…

data.chText: 在任何关系中，信任都是一个至关重要的因素。
data.enText: Trust is a vital component in any relationship.

data.chText: 将某物分成若干组成部分
data.enText: to break sth down into its component parts

simple_means.memory_skill: com 共同 + pon 放，放置 + ent 关于…的 → 共同放到一起 → 组成的

ex.chText: 他们是该组织中的先进分子。
ex.enText: They are advanced elements in the organization.

ex.chText: 速度是这一体育项目的要素。
ex.enText: Speed is an important element of the athletic event.

synonyms.bx: 尤指一整套系统、计划、作品等中最基本或最重要的成分或特征。

ex.enText: There are many components to the machine.

ex.chText: 该系统由各种部件组成。
ex.enText: This system consists of various components.

synonyms.bx: 指一个整体的组成部分，多用于机器、机械系统等。

ex.chText: 这种护肤霜只含天然成分。
ex.enText: This skin cream contains only natural ingredients.

ex.chText: 面粉和糖是烤面包最重要的原料。
ex.enText: Flour and sugar are the most important ingredients in baking bread.

synonyms.bx: 指混合物的成分，尤指烹饪原料。

tr: an artifact that is one of the individual parts of which a composite entity is made up
especially a part that can be separated from or attached to a system
example: a component or constituent element of a system
jealousy was a component of his character
two constituents of a musical composition are melody and harmony
the grammatical elements of a sentence
a key factor in her success
humor: an effective ingredient of a speech

tr: something determined in relation to something that includes it
example: he wanted to feel a part of something bigger than himself
I read a portion of the manuscript
the smaller component is hard to reach

value.def: The components of something are the parts that it is made of.

example.ex: Enriched uranium is a key component of a nuclear weapon...
example.tran: 浓缩铀是核武器的关键组成部分。

example.ex: The management plan has four main components...
example.tran: 管理计划有4个主要部分。

example.ex: They were automotive component suppliers to motor manufacturers.
example.tran: 他们为汽车制造商供应汽车零件。

value.def: The component parts of something are the parts that make it up.

example.ex: Gorbachev failed to keep the component parts of the Soviet Union together...
example.tran: 戈尔巴乔夫没能把苏联各成员国团结在一起。

example.ex: Polish workers will now be making component parts for Boeing 757s.
example.tran: 现在波音757飞机的组成部件将由波兰工人制造。
